verbose_text: In Dowa district, trials were established around Msakambewa trading centre (13degrees33 'S, 33degrees54'E) at 1200-1400 m above sea level (masl), in Mchinji around Kachamba village (13degrees44 'S, 33degrees20'E) at an altitude of 1050-1150 masl and in Salima around Chitala research station (13degrees40 'S, 34degrees15'E) at 550-650 masl.
